@startuml

title USEI04 - Pick Path Sequencing

autonumber

actor "Picker" as Picker
participant "Warehouse Management System" as WMS

activate Picker
Picker -> WMS: Requests picking path for a given plan
activate WMS

' The system validates the input picking plan
alt Empty or Invalid Picking Plan
    WMS --> Picker: Displays error message (e.g., "Picking plan is empty or invalid")

else Valid Picking Plan
    ' Internal processing steps based on Acceptance Criteria
    WMS -> WMS: Merge duplicate bay locations (AC1)
    
    ' Use a group to show the two main calculation tasks
    group Path Calculation for Both Strategies (AC2)
        WMS -> WMS: Calculate path using Strategy A (Deterministic Sweep)
        WMS -> WMS: Calculate path using Strategy B (Nearest-Neighbour)
    end
    
    ' The system returns the final, formatted result to the Picker
    WMS --> Picker: Displays both optimized paths and their total distances (AC3)
end

deactivate WMS
deactivate Picker

@enduml
